of implementing down regulation in coupled carbon-climate models in the absence of a more explicit biogeochemical representation. {\textcopyright} 2009 American Meteorological Society.},
author = {Arora, Vivek K and Boer, G J and Christian, J R and Curry, C L and Denman, K L and Zahariev, K and Flato, G M and Scinocca, J F and Merryfield, W J and Lee, W G},
